Class TarConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ice.tar.TarConstants

    Contains all of the constants we use for the tar files reading and writing. This library is under the Apache License Version 2.0 Authors:

      • OLDGNU_TMAGIC

        public static final java.lang.String OLDGNU_TMAGIC
        OLDGNU_MAGIC uses both magic and version fields, which are contiguous. Found in an archive, it indicates an old GNU header format, which will be hopefully become obsolete. With OLDGNU_MAGIC, uname and gname are valid, though the header is not truly POSIX conforming.
        See Also:
